{"tid":1717274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發覺高學歷既父母多數係黃?","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:28:58.000Z","uid":193217,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad2fc8a1760f6cfd3cb96152403a3ac6d194136","tid":1717274,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:34:18.000Z","msg":"而低學歷既就大部份藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似我老母為例.考大學時受到四人幫控制<br />\n連考試都係考住書黎考.佢講返比我聽.搞到唔想考<br />\n但到今日都居然話大陸非常好<br />\n呢種人大部份係因為比親戚茶毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似我老母為例<br />\n同佢地講道理真係晒氣<br />\n好彩既係佢無極端到見人就屌班細路<br />\n但次次佢一嘈.我就廢時同佢講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a4a20973a7bf9943633c09b2204853e122cc34","tid":1717274,"uid":209543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:35:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"399eed3db2914688a69dfe5b18ce12e8f4f1b339","tid":1717274,"uid":294447,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"唔關事<br />\n我老竇老母字都唔識隻<br />\n深黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c835b5e848a12a19bed4bdf18f4c876b85730dcb","tid":1717274,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"成日就話.依家大陸發展咁撚好<br />\n就算係普通農民有地都收返中共都比幾百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係呢種思想茶毒到佢地認為大陸咩都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"